cs213.photoAlbum.model

Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • cs213.photoAlbum.model.User
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class User
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Class User contains the information relating to a single user. The class contains the methods for adding, deleting and renaming an album.
    See Also:
